# Browser extension

- Manifest V3; minimal `host_permissions`; justify `<all_urls>` if ever required.
- Message passing: validate types; never `eval` remote code; no secrets in content scripts exposed to page.
- Review CSP and remote code policies; pin dependency versions for build tooling.
- Use `browser-extension-engineer` persona; security review before store publish.
